      "content": "that's a good start but it's a bit too formal. i need it to be more punchy for an essay. can u expand on the part about \"systemic disadvantages\"? like, how do we explain that the current system is basically rigged against people of color and why meritocracy is just a myth they use to keep things the way they are?",
